name: Sos(help me)
description:
Please help me by buying this NFT .... I explained my letter in my first full NFT
thank you
Please, because I do not have access to social networks, now I do not have friends who introduce me to the world, so you should be my friend and make my voice heard by everyone.
By buying this NFT, help us to match the necessary money that the Talabani man wants and we will not have to commit suicide.
Talabani says either I should be his wife when I am 12 or he will kill my parents unless we pay him $ 10,000.
